notes: 150 partnership (Kirsten, Boje) 156 balls, 90 minutes 2nd wicket record for RSA
Rain interupted the game for 90 minutes with the score at 22/1 off 4.2 overs
7 overs per side lost, new target 305 to win off 43 overs

milestones.description: Gary Kirsten and Nicky Boje's 160-run partnership is SA's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 149 between Hansie Cronje and Callaghan
